func: int PKCS7_add_attrib_smimecap(PKCS7_SIGNER_INFO *si, STACK_OF(X509_ALGOR) *cap) { ASN1_STRING *seq; if ((seq = ASN1_STRING_new()) == NULL) { PKCS7err(PKCS7_F_PKCS7_ADD_ATTRIB_SMIMECAP, ERR_R_MALLOC_FAILURE); return 0; } seq->length = ASN1_item_i2d((ASN1_VALUE *)cap, &seq->data, ASN1_ITEM_rptr(X509_ALGORS)); return PKCS7_add_signed_attribute(si, NID_SMIMECapabilities, V_ASN1_SEQUENCE, seq); }
